net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd

Class VerticalContainerDropTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd.VerticalContainerDropTarget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DropTarget

    public class VerticalContainerDropTarget
extends java.lang.Object
implements DropTarget
    A drop target to be used on components within a container. The components are meant to be laid out vertically, and the order of them can be reorganized via drag and drop.
    Author:
    Greg Dick (greg@i2rd.com)
